WEBVTT

00:06:27.689 --> 00:06:31.425
The lab banned Wite-Out --

00:06:31.449 --> 00:06:33.083
correction fluid --

00:06:33.107 --> 00:06:34.809
across its facility.

00:06:36.461 --> 00:06:41.601
Under FDA rules, data serves
as the cornerstone of quality.

00:06:42.213 --> 00:06:45.199
It has to be gathered
at each manufacturing step,

00:06:45.223 --> 00:06:46.374
preserved

00:06:46.398 --> 00:06:48.238
and shared with regulators.

00:06:48.783 --> 00:06:51.539
Wite-Out was high-risk.

00:06:51.563 --> 00:06:53.226
It invited tampering.

00:06:55.004 --> 00:07:00.473
It was clear that for the FDA's
regulatory regime to succeed,